# <type>(<scope>): <imperative summary — max 72 chars>
#
# Types: feat | fix | refactor | chore | docs | test | build | perf | deps
# Scope: overlay | bot-moderation | eventsub | sync-agent | discord |
#        counters | blazor | auth | infra | global | misc
#
# Body — bullet points, lines ≤ 100 chars (omit for trivial edits):
#
# - Key implementation moves
# - Why the change is needed
# - Side effects, migrations, or follow-up TODOs
# - BREAKING CHANGE: <description> (if applicable)
# - Tests: added | not-run | n/a
#
# Footer — always include one of:
#   Closes: #123        (resolves the issue — GitHub auto-closes on merge)
#   Refs: #123          (related but does not fully resolve)
#   Refs: None          (no issue)
#
Closes: #
